/*
 * Jon's custom Go60 keymap, adapted to run on the DONGLE (central).
 * Only change from the Go60 Layout Editor export: RGB underglow bindings are
 * replaced with &trans (the XIAO dongle has no LEDs and &rgb_ug would not link).
 * All layers, homerow mods, mouse layer, and trackpad scaling are unchanged.
